   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:span text:style-name="T6">6</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">. Vasile Băncilă, Duhul sărbătorii, Bucureşti, Editura Anastasia, 1996, p. 56</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:span text:style-name="T6">7</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">. Lucian Blaga, Opere 9. Trilogia culturii, Bucureşti, Editura Minerva, 1985, p. 270</text:span></text:p>
