   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:span text:style-name="T6">1</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">2. Olivier Clement, Puterea credinţei, Târgovişte, Editura Pandora, 1999, p. 21</text:span></text:p>
